          %h1 Gateway Commercial Finance's Accessibility Statement
          %p Updated: December 2019
          
          %h3 General
          %p Gateway Commercial Finance strives to ensure that its services are accessible to   people with disabilities. Gateway Commercial Finance has invested a significant   amount of resources to help ensure that its website is made easier to use and more accessible for people with disabilities, with the strong belief that every person has the right to live with dignity, equality,  comfort and independence.
          %h3 Accessibility on Gateway Commercial Finance's Websites
          %p Gatewaycfs.com makes available the <a href="https://UserWay.org" alt="Free Website Accessibility Widget" title="Free Website Accessibility Widget">UserWay Website Accessibility Widget</a> that is powered by a dedicated accessibility server. The software allows Gatewaycfs.com to improve its compliance with the Web Content  Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG 2.1).
          %br/
          %h3 Enabling the Accessibility Menu
          %p The Gateway Commercial Finance's website accessibility menu can be enabled by clicking the accessibility menu icon that appears on the corner of the page. After triggering the accessibility menu, please wait a moment for the accessibility menu to load in its entirety.
          %h3 Disclaimer
          %p Gateway Commercial Finance continues its efforts to constantly improve the   accessibility of its site and services in the belief that it is our collective moral obligation to allow seamless, accessible and unhindered  use also for those of us with disabilities.
          %p Despite our efforts to make all pages and content on Gateway Commercial Finance's websites fully accessible, some content may not have yet been fully adapted to  the strictest accessibility standards. This may be a result of not having found or identified the most appropriate technological solution.
          %br/
          %h3 Here For You
          %p If you are experiencing difficulty with any content on Gateway Commercial Finance's websites or require assistance with any part of our site, please contact us during normal business hours as detailed below and we will be happy to assist.
          %h3 Contact Us
          %p If you wish to report an accessibility issue, have any questions or need assistance, please contact our Customer Support as follows:
          %br/
          Email: marketing (at) gatewaycfs.com
                

